Commands.label: Commands
Commands.tooltip: Words the bot will be looking for, leave a space between each word to add more.

OutputMessage.label: Output Message
OutputMessage.tooltip: The output message for this command. $match_type will be PartialMatch, Exact Match, etc. $item_name will be the name that was found on the wiki. $quest_strings will be the name of the quests

CommandCooldown.label: Command Cooldown
CommandCooldown.tooltip: How often someone can use this command in chat
